---
title: "Credit Investment Memo - L0 Overview"
---
flowchart TD
    classDef llmFull fill:#2E7D32,stroke:#1B5E20,color:#fff,rx:4,ry:4
    classDef llmPartial fill:#E65100,stroke:#BF360C,color:#fff,rx:4,ry:4
    classDef llmNone fill:#C62828,stroke:#B71C1C,color:#fff,rx:4,ry:4
    classDef gate fill:#F9A825,stroke:#F57F17,color:#1a202c,font-weight:bold,rx:4,ry:4
    classDef decision fill:#1565C0,stroke:#0D47A1,color:#fff,rx:12,ry:12
    classDef endpoint fill:#6A1B9A,stroke:#4A148C,color:#fff,rx:20,ry:20
    classDef killPath fill:#B71C1C,stroke:#880E4F,color:#fff,rx:20,ry:20,font-weight:bold
    classDef output fill:#0D47A1,stroke:#0A3A7E,color:#fff,rx:4,ry:4

    %% PHASE 1
    ENTRY_A([Analyst identifies credit via screen, broker, or new issue]):::endpoint
    ENTRY_PM([PM assigns issuer coverage or flags spread opportunity]):::endpoint

    ENTRY_A --> PH1
    ENTRY_PM --> PH1

    PH1[Phase 1: Opportunity Screening and Mandate Fit]:::llmPartial
    PH1 --> D1{Go / No-Go?}:::decision
    D1 -->|No-Go| PASS([Log reason and pass]):::endpoint
    D1 -->|Go| PH1_OUT[Phase 1 Output: Approved credit screen, preliminary thesis, risk list]:::output

    %% PARALLEL SPLIT
    PH1_OUT --> PH2
    PH1_OUT --> PH3
    PH1_OUT --> PH4

    %% PHASE 2
    PH2[Phase 2: Issuer and Industry Analysis]:::llmFull
    PH2 --> PH2_OUT[Phase 2 Output: Industry context, issuer profile, downturn scenarios]:::output

    %% PHASE 3 with kill paths
    PH3[Phase 3: Credit Financial Analysis]:::llmPartial
    PH3 --> D_FCF{FCF conversion consistently below 50 pct?}:::decision
    D_FCF -->|Yes| KILL_FCF([DEAL KILLER: Cash generation structurally impaired]):::killPath
    D_FCF -->|No| PH3_OK[Phase 3 continues: Liquidity and covenant analysis]:::llmPartial
    PH3_OK -.->|GAAP vs covenant EBITDA mismatch| KILL_COV([DEAL KILLER: Headroom calculation dangerously wrong]):::killPath
    PH3_OK --> PH3_OUT[Phase 3 Output: Standardized financials, liquidity model, covenant analysis]:::output

    %% PHASE 4 with kill path
    PH4[Phase 4: Legal and Structural Analysis]:::llmPartial
    PH4 --> D_LME{Material structural deficiencies identified?}:::decision
    D_LME -->|Yes| KILL_LME([DEAL KILLER: Structurally unsafe debt]):::killPath
    D_LME -->|No| PH4_OUT[Phase 4 Output: Covenant quality, structural protections, LME risk]:::output

    %% Phase 2 feeds Phase 4 structural subordination
    PH2_OUT --> PH4_OUT

    %% CONVERGENCE INTO PHASE 5
    PH2_OUT --> PH23_CONVERGE[Phases 2 and 3 converge]:::output
    PH3_OUT --> PH23_CONVERGE
    PH23_CONVERGE --> PH5
    PH4_OUT -->|Recovery and covenant inputs| PH5

    %% PHASE 5
    PH5[Phase 5: Credit Modeling and Scenario Analysis]:::llmPartial
    PH5 --> PH5_OUT[Phase 5 Output: Cash flow projections, debt waterfall, recovery, expected return]:::output

    %% PHASE 6
    PH5_OUT --> PH6
    PH6[Phase 6: Relative Value Analysis]:::llmPartial
    PH6 --> PH6_OUT[Phase 6 Output: Comparable spreads, total return matrix, rate factor decomposition]:::output

    %% CONVERGENCE INTO PHASE 7
    PH4_OUT --> PH_PREFR[All analysis complete, ready for data freeze]:::output
    PH6_OUT --> PH_PREFR

    %% PHASE 7
    PH_PREFR --> PH7
    PH7[Phase 7: Data Freeze Gate]:::llmNone
    PH7 --> D_FREEZE{Data Freeze Gate: All items passed?}:::gate
    D_FREEZE -->|No| PH7_FIX[Resolve gaps and re-verify]:::llmNone
    PH7_FIX --> D_FREEZE
    D_FREEZE -->|Yes| PH7_OUT[Phase 7 Output: Frozen data package, version-stamped model]:::output

    %% PHASE 8
    PH7_OUT --> PH8
    PH8[Phase 8: Memo Drafting]:::llmFull
    PH8 -.->|Spread moves over 50bps or material issuer event| PH8_UF[Un-freeze, update model, re-freeze]:::llmNone
    PH8_UF -.-> PH8
    PH8 --> PH8_OUT[Phase 8 Output: Complete credit memo draft with all sections]:::output

    %% PHASE 9
    PH8_OUT --> PH9
    PH9[Phase 9: Quality Assurance and Review]:::llmFull
    PH9 --> D_COLD{Cold reader approves?}:::decision
    D_COLD -->|Sends back| PH9_REV[Analyst: Revise per cold reader comments]:::llmFull
    PH9_REV --> PH9
    D_COLD -->|Approved| PH9_OUT[Phase 9 Output: Final memo, version-stamped and cold-reader approved]:::output

    %% PHASE 10
    PH9_OUT --> PH10
    PH10[Phase 10: IC Preparation and Execution]:::llmNone
    PH10 --> D_IC{IC decision?}:::decision
    D_IC -->|Reject| ARCHIVE([Document rationale and archive]):::endpoint
    D_IC -->|Revisions| PH_PREFR
    D_IC -->|Approve| S10_4[PM to Ops and Trading: Document IC decision and execute trade]:::llmNone
    S10_4 --> TRADE_DONE([Position established]):::endpoint

    %% PHASE 11
    TRADE_DONE -.->|Recurring at each reporting period| PH11
    PH11[Phase 11: Ongoing Position Monitoring]:::llmPartial
    PH11 --> D_THESIS{Thesis status?}:::decision
    D_THESIS -->|INTACT| MONITOR([Next review cycle]):::endpoint
    D_THESIS -->|REVISED| UPDATE[Analyst + PM: Update position parameters and exit criteria]:::llmNone
    UPDATE --> MONITOR
    D_THESIS -->|BROKEN| SELL([Trigger sell discipline per Phase 8 exit criteria]):::endpoint

    %% PHASE 12
    TRADE_DONE -.->|Annual portfolio-wide review| PH12
    PH12[Phase 12: Post-Mortem - Annual Process Review]:::llmPartial
    PH12 --> PM_IMPROVE([Process and framework improvements institutionalized]):::endpoint
